UID:_BWGycBcbNNhPMsLvOy4g
SUMMARY:Show Your Game: An Improvised Game Show
DTSTAMP:20260328T110949Z
DTSTART:20260329T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Sundays in March! A Comedy Game Show About Ridiculously Specifi
	c Expertise. Everyone is secretly an expert at something. In Show Your Gam
	e \, professional improvisers and fearless audience volunteers step into t
	he worlds of real-life experts and attempt to survive challenges designed 
	by those experts. Expect strange trivia\, impossible tasks\, wildly specif
	ic knowledge\, and the kind of confidence that only comes from being compl
	etely wrong in public. Maybe it’s acupuncture. Maybe it’s panic packing. M
	aybe it’s Gilmore Girls . Maybe it’s finding creative new places to lose y
	our keys. Inspired by the chaotic brilliance of Taskmaster \, the clever c
	uriosity of QI \, and the unpredictable madness of Game Changer \, every s
	how is completely improvised and completely different. Past topics have in
	cluded haunting\, bubbles\, bedtime routines\, public art\, computer progr
	amming\, low-income housing\, tabletop RPG streaming\, Veggie Tales\, hous
	esitting disasters\, and one unforgettable investigation into a s\n\nhttps
	://www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/show-your-game-an-improvised-ga
	me-show-2/?occurrence=2026-03-29\n\nFrom Pike Place Market Events
URL:https://www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/show-your-game-an-impro
	vised-game-show-2/?occurrence=2026-03-29
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\, 1428 Post Alley
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:events
CATEGORIES:Pike Place Market Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:kp_Pzi8gC5UORqK0m6pQa
SUMMARY:Show Your Game: An Improvised Game Show
DTSTAMP:20260328T110949Z
DTSTART:20260329T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:Ever wonder what secret skills your neighbors are hiding? That 
	quiet person next to you on the bus might be a brain surgeon\\\, a barbecu
	e champion\\\, or the only parent in town who can get their toddler to nap
	 on time. Show Your Game is here to celebrate those everyday experts and u
	nexpected talents! \\nEach night\\\, a hilarious mix of improvisers and br
	ave audience members go head-to-head\\\, diving deep into the worlds of tw
	o surprising experts. They’ll tackle quirky questions and wild challenges\
	\\, each crafted by the experts themselves to test just how much our conte
	stants really know. \\nLove the clever chaos of QI\\\, the unpredictable t
	wists of Game Changer\\\, or the absurd fun of Taskmaster? Then this is yo
	ur kind of show. \\nSo\\\, when it’s your turn to step into someone else’s
	 world… are you ready to Show Your Game?\n\nhttps://www.unexpectedproducti
	ons.org/event/show-your-game-an-improvised-game-show-3/2026-03-29/\n\nFrom
	 Unexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/show-your-game-an-improvise
	d-game-show-3/2026-03-29/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\\\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike
	 Place Market\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98101\\\, United States
